<h2>Common Workflow Patterns</h2>

<h3>Basic Infrastructure Deployment</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Use <strong>Stacks</strong> to deploy foundational infrastructure</li>
  <li>Use <strong>Assertions</strong> to validate the deployment</li>
  <li>Use <strong>Lambda Invocations</strong> for post-deployment configuration</li>
</ol>

<h3>Service Catalog Hub-and-Spoke</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Create portfolios and products in the hub account</li>
  <li>Use <strong>Spoke Local Portfolios</strong> to distribute to spoke accounts</li>
  <li>Use <strong>Launches</strong> to provision products in target accounts</li>
  <li>Use <strong>Assertions</strong> to validate product deployments</li>
</ol>

<h3>Governance and Compliance</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Set up <strong>Organizational Units</strong> for account hierarchy</li>
  <li>Apply <strong>Service Control Policies</strong> for security boundaries</li>
  <li>Implement <strong>Tag Policies</strong> for standardization</li>
  <li>Use <strong>C7N AWS Lambdas</strong> for automated compliance</li>
  <li>Use <strong>Assertions</strong> to validate compliance status</li>
</ol>

